  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;Results for Development will research how evidence is translated between producers and users in the evidence-informed policymaking ecosystem. The research will include a map of translators in East and West Africa; a framework and typologies that describe their activities, contextual constraints, and enabling factors; and characteristics that influence their success. It will also include ethnographic case studies. &quot;</narrative>
  </description>
